Title: Requires the commissioner of parks, recreation and historic preservation to issue guidance for the receipt of certain state aid
Summary: Requires the commissioner of parks, recreation and historic preservation to issue guidance for the receipt of certain state aid by eligible governmental agencies related to enforcement of the state navigation law.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the navigation law, in relation to requiring the commissioner of parks, recreation and historic preservation to issue guidance for the receipt of certain state aid
